body.paragraph:
‘‘Dveme , bhikkhave, santhārāsandhārā 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='2', original='sandhārā (ka.)', type='auto', previous=', bhikkhave, santhārā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='santhārā'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='sandhārā'}}
. Katame dve? Āmisasanthāro ca dhammasanthāro ca. Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve santhārā. Etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ dvinnaṃ santhārānaṃ yadidaṃ dhammasanthāro’’ti.

 ‘‘Dveme, bhikkhave, paṭisanthārāpaṭisandhārā 
Note { id=1, line='12', referenceLine='3', original='paṭisandhārā (ka.)', type='auto', previous=' Dveme, bhikkhave, paṭisanthārā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='paṭisanthārā'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='paṭisandhārā'}}
. Katame dve? Āmisapaṭisanthāro ca dhammapaṭisanthāro ca. Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve paṭisanthārā. Etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ dvinnaṃ paṭisanthārānaṃ yadidaṃ dhammapaṭisanthāro’’ti.
